item.title: Hack The Box: Luke Writeup | Medium
item.description: Hack The Box: Luke Writeup Welcome to my detailed writeup of the medium difficulty machine “Luke” on Hack The Box. This writeup will cover the steps taken to achieve initial foothold and escalation to root.
